translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 門番の器兵が襲ってきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The gatekeeper automaton attacked.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中、器兵（アスタコプロト）　２ターン目、割り込み
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: During battle, Automaton (Astacoprot), turn 2, interrupt.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 強いぞ、コレ・・これまで見た器兵より複雑な動きをしやがる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's strong... It moves more complexly than any automaton I've seen before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マリア、すごいなぁ、ほんと。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maria, you're amazing, really.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 歯車とゼンマイだけでこの自律行動、職人芸だなぁ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This autonomous behavior with only gears and springs is true craftsmanship.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こらこら、感心してないで戦え！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey hey, don't admire it, fight!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中、器兵（アスタコプロト）　６ターン目、割り込み
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: During battle, Automaton (Astacoprot), turn 6, interrupt.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ん、なんか動きがおかしくなってきたぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, its movements are getting strange.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カクカクと同じ動きをしている、なんだ？罠か・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's moving jerkily in the same way. What's this? A trap...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マリア、うーん残念、不具合が発生しているようね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maria, hmm, unfortunately, it seems a malfunction has occurred.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これだけ複雑な物だし、攻撃で衝撃も受けているからしかたないかもだけど
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's such a complex machine, and it's taken impacts from attacks, so maybe it can't be helped.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もったいない、ちょっとまって私修理を
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a waste, wait a moment, I'll repair it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なにをいっている、いまのうちに潰すぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What are you saying? We'll crush it while we still can.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 中からエロい声が聞こえる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lewd voices can be heard from inside.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 門を開けてランス達は中に入った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They opened the gate and Rance and his group entered inside.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 街中に入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Entering the town.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ポピンズ達の青姦乱交パーティ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Poppins and their outdoor group orgy party.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 満鉄王に同盟を持ちかける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Propose an alliance to the Mantetsu King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 条件１．アニャガスとは嫌
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Condition 1: Do not want to ally with Anyagas.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 条件２．娘の日立を探して出してくれ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Condition 2: Find and release his daughter Hitachi.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 日立が砂漠案内人と思い出す、砂漠へ向かう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Remember that Hitachi is the desert guide, head toward the desert.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: キナニ砂漠で日立姫と会う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meet Princess Hitachi in the Kinani Desert.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東芝王子とのロミオとジュリエット話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A Romeo and Juliet story with Prince Toshiba.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東芝王子と会いたい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Want to meet Prince Toshiba.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東芝王子を助ける事に決めた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Decided to help Prince Toshiba.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここでクリームがウルザと交代
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here, Cream switches out for Urza.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マルグリッド迷宮から
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From the Marguerite Maze.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アニャガス王国を目指す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Head toward the Anyagas Kingdom.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ポピンズの警備隊が居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There's a Poppins security guard.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞合流に向かった場合
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > When heading to the meetup.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ、お前は連続誘拐拉致監禁犯！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, you're the serial kidnapper, abductor, and captor!
